  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "因为我还没有拿出来。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 26
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuang_jia",
    "speaker_name": "庄家",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我们这里的规矩，要看见银子才算数。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 28
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuang_jia",
    "speaker_name": "庄家",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你用这把刀押五百两？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 32
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "嗯。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 34
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuang_jia",
    "speaker_name": "庄家",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我好像看不出这刀能值五百两。",
