    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 64
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_sha_man",
    "text": "我借给你，只不过你好像替我带来点运气，这一注我又押得特别多，所以不想让你走而已。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 66
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "统杀！",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 70
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "六",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 74
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "么",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 74
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_sha_man",
    "text": "你虽然为我带来点运气，你自己的运气却不好。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 110
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我们都是小胡子，我们交个朋友。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 128
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "仗义勇为",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 130
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "刀呢？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 132
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "什么刀？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 134
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "像你刚才那样的刀。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 136
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "像那样的刀，找遍天下恐怕也只有一把。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 138
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "么二三",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 140
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "手气如何？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 148
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "还不算太坏，只不过该赢的没有赢，不该输的却输了。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 150
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "世上有很多事都是这样子的，倘若是对一样事情太有把握了，反而会疏忽，所以该赢的会输，但是只要还有第二次机会，就一定可以把握住了。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 152
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "你若肯投资，让我去赌，赢了我们对分。",
