    "line_num": 318
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我本来不常喝的，现在好像受了你的传染。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 320
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "好，我敬你三杯。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 322
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "三杯只怕就醉了。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 324
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "一醉解千愁，人生难得几回醉，来，喝。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 326
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你年纪轻轻的，有什么愁？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 328
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "我输的虽然是别人的钱财，心里还是难免有点难受。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 332
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "那可不是别人的钱财，是你的。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 334
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "真是我的？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 336
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我既然已将银子借给了你，当然就是你的。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 338
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "想不到你竟是个如此慷慨的人。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 340
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "慷他人之慨，本就算不了什么，只不过……",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 344
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "银子虽然是你的，你的人却已是我的。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 348
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我姓陆，你姓吴，你既不是我儿子，我也不是你老子，我怎么会是你的？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 350
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "因为你还不出一万五千两，就只好将你的人赔给我，丈夫一言，快马一鞭，为了成全你的信誉，我想不要都不行。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 352
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "我这人又好酒，又好色，又好吃，又好赌，花起钱财来像流水一样，我若是你的，你就得养我。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 356
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我养得起。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 358
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "可是我倒想不通，你要我这么样一个大混蛋干什么？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 360
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我的银子太多，正想找个人帮我花花，免得我自己受罪。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 364
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "你认为花钱是在受罪？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 366
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "怎么不是受罪？若是喝得太多，第二天头疼如裂，就像生了场大病，若是赌得太凶，非但神经紧张，如坐针毡，手气不来时，说不定还会被活活气死，若是纵情声色……",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 370
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_接",
    "speaker_name": "接",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这种对身体有伤的事，像我这种年纪的人，更是连提都不敢提。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 372
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "除了花钱外，你还准备要我干什么？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 374
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你年纪轻轻，身体强健，武功又不错，我可以要你做的事，也不知有多少。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 376
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "武功又不弱",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 378
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "化骨绵掌",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 386
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "指刀",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 386
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "现在你心里一定已经在后悔，觉得自己不该来的，却又偏偏猜不出我们究竟在玩什么花样，难免动了好奇，所以又舍不得走。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 400
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "不对不对，完全不对。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 404
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "什么事不对？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 406
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "你说的完全不对。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 408
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "这里有酒有肉，又有天仙般的美女，还有准备给银子让我花的人，我还有什么不满意的？为什么要后悔？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 410
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "因为你心里还在嘀咕，猜不透我究竟要你干什么？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 412
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "像我这样的人，还有什么不能干的？就算要我去杀人，我也一刀一个，而且还绝不管埋。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 416
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "真的？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 418
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "当然是真的！",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 420
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_微笑着",
    "speaker_name": "微笑着",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "只要你能记住今天的话，我保证你一辈子平安快乐。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 422
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "化骨绵掌",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 426
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_微笑着",
    "speaker_name": "微笑着",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "指刀",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 426
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "这里的牛是不是也跟你的银子一样多？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 436
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "今天做的本是全牛宴，因为小女特别喜欢吃牛肉。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 438
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "其实她别的地方也并不怪，只不过每顿饭非牛肉不吃，吃了十几年，也吃不腻，若有人认为她是怪物，那就错了。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 446
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "我心里在想什么，你都知道？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 450
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "这种察言观色的本事，我倒也不敢妄自菲薄。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 454
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "你知道我现在心里在想什么？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 456
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你本来想故意去想些稀奇古怪的事，好来难倒我，可是你又偏偏忍不住想要看看我那专吃牛肉的女儿。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 458
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_sha_man",
    "text": "不对不对，你女儿又不嫁给我，我去看她干什么？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 462
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "今天她是主客，为什么反而一直踪影不见？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 466
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "她是谁？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 468
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_sha_man",
    "text": "她就是你女儿。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 470
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你既然连看都不想看她，问她干什么？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 472
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "只可惜你就算真的不想看见她，迟早还是会看见她的。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 478
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_sha_man",
    "text": "我不想看见她都不行？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 480
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "不行。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 482
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_sha_man",
    "text": "为什么？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 484
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "因为你现在只要一回头，就已看见她了。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 486
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你认得她？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 506
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_sha_man",
    "text": "本来我以前是认得她的。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 508
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "现在呢？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 510
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_sha_man",
    "text": "现在看起来，她也不认得我，我也不认得她。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 514
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我叫你早点去睡的，你怎么偏偏又要溜出来？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 518
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我听丫头说，刚才外面有人回来，却不知有没有九哥的消息？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 520
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你猜呢？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 522
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "我知道一定有，九哥绝不会忘了我的。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 524
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
    "speaker_name": "小老头",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我本来想明天早上再告诉你，老九不但有消息带回来，还叫他新收的随从木一半带了些礼物回来给你。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 526
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "这个木一半的人呢？赶快叫他来，把九哥的礼物也带来。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 528
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我听九哥说起过，你一定就是木一半了。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 538
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_sha_man",
    "text": "小人木一半，参见公主。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 540
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "九哥又不是不知道我不稀罕这些东西，为什么偏偏的叫你送来？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 550
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "公主再看看这三口箱子里面是什么？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 554
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "铁掌金刀",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 562
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "四大高僧",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 566
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "怪事年年有，今年特别多，箱子里怎么会忽然钻出个和尚！",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 578
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "text": "小姑娘受了气，大和尚进箱子，阿弥勒佛！善哉善哉！",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 580
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_yi_ban",
    "speaker_name": "木一半",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "九少爷知道这三个人得罪过公主，所以要小人赶紧送来，好让公主出气。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 582
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "text": "却不知公主想怎么样出气？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 588
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我一时倒还没有想起来，你替我出个主意怎么样？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 590
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_yi_ban",
    "speaker_name": "木一半",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这就要看公主是想大出气，还是小出气了。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 592
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "小出气怎么样？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 596
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_yi_ban",
    "speaker_name": "木一半",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "脱下他们的裤子来，重重的打个七八十板，也就是了。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 598
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "大出气呢？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 600
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_yi_ban",
    "speaker_name": "木一半",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "割下他们的脑袋来，晒干了赏给小人下酒。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 602
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "text": "好主意，真是好主意，难怪九哥喜欢你。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 606
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我们既然已落在你手里，要杀要剐，绝不皱一皱眉头，你若是故意羞侮我，我……我死了也不饶你！",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 614
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "我死了也不饶你",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 616
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_牛肉汤嫣然",
    "speaker_name": "牛肉汤嫣然",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你活着也不能对我怎么样，死了又能怎么样不饶我？难道想变成个大头鬼，半夜来扼我脖子？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 618
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "text": "好功夫！",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 626
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这只不过是如意兰花手中最简单的一着，算不了什么好功夫！",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 628
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "你……你连死都不让我死？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 634
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "好死不如歹活，你为什么偏偏想死？就算你自知得罪了我，犯了死罪，也可以找个人来替你死的。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 638
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "怎么替我死？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 642
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "这里的人你可以随便挑一个，只要能胜得了他一招半式，我就要他替你死。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 644
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_yi_ban",
    "speaker_name": "木一半",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这里的人我看他连一个都不敢找。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 646
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "一个人他不敢找，半个人呢？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 650
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我算来算去，他最多也只能找我这半个人。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 652
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "不错，我正是要找你。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 656
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "笑指天南",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 668
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "嗤，嗤，嗤",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 670
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "好剑法。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 674
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "这只不过是天残十三式中简单的三招，算不了什么好剑法。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 678
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "罗寨主的‘燕子飞云纵’和一着‘飞燕去来’，纵横天下，杀人无数，我也久仰得很了，却不知罗寨主是否也看上了我这半个人？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 690
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "飞燕去来",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 692
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "飞燕去来",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 696
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "醉卧流云七杀手，惟有饮者得真传，贺尚书真好功夫。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 708
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "木一半真好眼力，连绝传已八十年的醉中七杀手都能看得出。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 712
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "text": "一杀就已要了命，又何必七杀？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 714
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
    "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "text": "和尚也想试试？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 716
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "和尚还清醒得很，为什么要去跟醉鬼纠缠？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 718
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你准备找谁？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 720
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_yi_ban",
    "speaker_name": "木一半",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "是不是想找我？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 722
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "和尚至少还是一个人，不跟半个人斗。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 724
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我是一个人。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 726
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "和尚至少还是个大男人，不跟女人斗。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 728
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我爹爹是个男人。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 730
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "和尚还年轻力壮，不跟老头子斗。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 732
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你看那几个人怎么样？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 738
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "和尚四大皆空，看见赌鬼们就害怕。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 740
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "text": "你左挑右选都看不中，倒不如让我来替你选一个。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 744
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "谁？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 746
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_sha_man",
    "text": "你看他怎么样？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 748
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "和尚说老实话，和尚若是想活命，好像也只有选他了。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 754
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "原来和尚的眼力也不差。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 756
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "差差，简直差上十万八千里。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 760
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "差在哪里？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 762
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "我跟这和尚是朋友，他绝不会想要我的命，我也不想要他的命。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 764
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "和尚本来的确不想要你命的，可是现在……",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 766
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "别人的性命再珍贵，总不如自己的性命重要，和尚这条命再不值钱，好歹总是和尚自己的。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 768
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "text": "可是和尚既然四大皆空，若连朋友的命都要，岂非大错特错，大差特差？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 772
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好死不如歹活，活狗也能咬死狮子几口，到了性命交关时，就算差一点，也说不得了。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 774
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "text": "你为什么不去找别人，偏偏要找上我？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 776
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "因为你差。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 778
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "text": "我差在哪里？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 780
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你既不会‘天残十三式’，又不会‘如意兰花手’，岂非大差特差？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 782
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "text": "可是我并不想要你的命。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 784
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "你不想要和尚的命，和尚却想要你的命，所以你更差得厉害，非死不可。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 786
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "他这样的人，多死一个少一个，你还不动手？",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 788
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
    "text": "姑娘说的是，和尚这就动手。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 790
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_忽然",
    "speaker_name": "忽然",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "陆小凤，你是要替这和尚死，还是要替自己留着这条命，你可得仔细想清楚。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 798
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wu_ming",
    "text": "嘶",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 802
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "和尚若是再不住手，小和尚只怕就要露出来了。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 808
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "text": "小和尚露面，总比大和尚挺尸好。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 814
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_man",
    "speaker_name": "沙曼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "想不到和尚还会蒙古人摔跤的功夫。",
    "tone": "普通",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_num": 824
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
    "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
